{"tid":883053,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食譜]—芝士白汁雞肉三文治 Hot Brown","createTime":"2018-10-30T14:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T13:28:36.000Z","uid":182683,"like":57,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b1cd535a36996c1204d248f829e491f1c00ff092","tid":883053,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"我個igtv有片睇！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/Bpjx-Hynn10/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1dpgqurgnk3kb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FBpjx-Hynn10%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D1dpgqurgnk3kb&d=4yQ6pjSs0bH3JieQ0wn1pSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1936c014\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/Bpjx-Hynn10/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1dpgqurgnk3kb</a><br />\n今次整個三高早餐比大家試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，係美國一個好傳統比職安真漢子食嘅早餐，做法極簡單！食完飽到包你全日都唔駛食呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215036_e83c9886826261f1461e0c390f97a908.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215036_e83c9886826261f1461e0c390f97a908.png&h=7ad8107f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n雞胸肉 1塊(用咩部位雞肉都得,我自己用隔夜食剩嘅雞胸肉）<br />\n蕃茄仔 5-6粒<br />\n方包 2片 <br />\n煙肉 2片 <br />\n香芹 少少<br />\n芝士碎(Pecorino Romano) 少少<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n芝士白汁(Mornay sauce):<br />\n牛油 1湯匙 <br />\n麵粉 1湯匙 <br />\n凍牛奶 240-280毫升(睇你鐘意杰定稀）<br />\n芝士碎(Pecorino Romano) 大概2.5湯匙<br />\n鹽 自己試味<br />\n黑胡椒 自己試味<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n做法：<br />\n1.煮芝士白汁(Mornay sauce)<br />\n中細火，溶左啲牛油先，跟住落麵粉攪到變左一篤糊仔咁(roux)。<br />\n轉中火，落1/3凍牛奶，攪到個汁滑身冇曬一粒粒就可以落埋其餘個啲奶，滾起左滑身同杰就可以熄火，落芝士碎，鹽同胡椒調味，攪混就搞掂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215057_f277654d4db10bbbe649be74a1450328.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215057_f277654d4db10bbbe649be74a1450328.png&h=6356a74e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215100_84bee099863a60a4d8038700b3de8670.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215100_84bee099863a60a4d8038700b3de8670.png&h=8bd5db90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.煎香雞肉,煙肉,麵包,備料<br />\n焗爐剩係開上面個火，開到最大預熱。<br />\n講講個雞肉先，用咩位都得嘅，唔駛一定要新鮮雞肉，我自己就用隔夜食剩嘅雞胸肉，切厚塊煎一煎香佢。<br />\n煙肉又係煎熟，煎到7-8成熟到。<br />\n麵包就用牛油煎到兩面金黃色同脆，去邊切三角形。<br />\n蕃茄仔開半，落少少鹽。<br />\n香芹菜切碎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215150_a546e4546dd69ae656334f526e5e8ce3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215150_a546e4546dd69ae656334f526e5e8ce3.png&h=5e7efcec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215154_cf4ab8c395fe18f0ebfdcde84bc98d8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215154_cf4ab8c395fe18f0ebfdcde84bc98d8d.png&h=a30d13f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215155_f60d4ecb80161504cb1c63eba3c3ee9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215155_f60d4ecb80161504cb1c63eba3c3ee9a.png&h=fc30d7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.入爐<br />\n拎個入得爐嘅兜，雞肉放中間，麵包放四邊圍住，再淋汁上去啲雞肉到，如果個汁太杰就熱一熱先用，放埋啲蕃茄仔，再撒啲芝士碎上個汁到，最後放埋煙肉係面，入爐焗到啲芝士燶燶地就搞掂。<br />\n出爐撒埋啲香芹碎，搞掂！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215255_c7f1c85203aa8531728500465ea4fbc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215255_c7f1c85203aa8531728500465ea4fbc3.png&h=c75f46d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215257_d004c64ed54a7a41bf1a0e35377a22a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215257_d004c64ed54a7a41bf1a0e35377a22a2.png&h=8db1017a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215300_662f13478138a0a047782cc1dd4267e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215300_662f13478138a0a047782cc1dd4267e6.png&h=c85ddd26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/215309_e170e5fa7799097577aad451844d9dfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F215309_e170e5fa7799097577aad451844d9dfd.png&h=1aa19d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n難易度：2/5&ndash;個汁唔好起粒<br />\n溝女指數：3/5&ndash;又芝士又極濃又流心又拉絲又鬼佬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=4yQ6pjSs0bH3JieQ0wn1pSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f7ba9672\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eca6d7e7cfcef491508b1fd1071ed1b3aa241f6","tid":883053,"uid":13845,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:03:04.000Z","msg":"樓主食完小心生癌"},{"pid":"47dee103479f769c99d2de8a351bc5c36c5564e5","tid":883053,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06516fb9e9c276ef8cd5158e4b19471c842593e4","tid":883053,"uid":13845,"lik